[8] https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep
[9] https://github.com/tmux/tmux
[10] https://github.com/ajeetdsouza/zoxide
[11] https://github.com/eth-p/bat-extras
[12] https://github.com/ghostty-org/ghostty
